# Autonomous Research Agent

## Overview
An AI-powered research agent built using LangChain that:
- Searches the web
- Extracts insights
- Generates structured reports

## Features
- ReAct-based agent
- Web + Wikipedia tools
- Automated report generation

## How to Run
```bash
python main.py

